workshop.tools.svm.mal.js.detector

Class SVM_Detector

  • java.lang.Object
    • workshop.tools.svm.mal.js.detector.SVM_Detector

  • public class SVM_Detector
extends java.lang.Object
    SVM detector as proposed by the paper:

    "A Static Malicious Javascript Detection Using SVM"

    Written by:

    WANG Wei-Hong, LV Yin-Jun, CHEN Hui-Bing and FANG Zhao-Lin,

    Zhejiang University of Technology HangZhou, China.
